AU  - Wang, Li-yuan
AU  - Ma, Ying
AU  - Shao, Fang
AU  - Ma, Jia
TI  - Market analysis and market outlook of Shanghai aquatic products under the background of improving quality and efficiency.
T2  - Acta Agriculturae Shanghai
M3  - Journal article
AB  - As an important aquatic product consumer market in China, Shanghai's aquatic product market analysis and market outlook have important significance for China's aquatic product market. In 2018, affected by the factors of natural disasters at the end of culture, the multiple policy factors and the demand factors of consumer-end aquatic products market, the prices of Shanghai's aquatic products were running at a high level with an upward trend, and the trading volume showed a downward trend. It is expected that in the context of adjustment of improving quality and increasing efficiency in aquatic product market, the supply of aquatic products gradually tends to be stable in the later stage. The diversification of the consumer market and the escalation of consumption regularization will lead to a large increase in the price of high-grade seafood and a moderate increase in aquatic product prices as a whole. In order to stabilize the sustainable and effective promotion of improving quality and efficiency of the aquatic product market in the future, some relevant policy recommendations are proposed, including promoting the optimization of aquaculture structure, upgrading the processing technology of aquatic products, strengthening the construction of market early warning system, innovating "Internet +" fisheries, and maintaining trade stability in the international market.
PU  - Editorial Office of Acta Agriculturae Shanghai
PA  - Shanghai
DA  - 2020
