TI  - Breeding of new high-yield, high-sugar and lodging-resistant sugarcane variety Guitang 42 and its high-yield cultivation technique.
T2  - Journal of Southern Agriculture
M3  - Journal article
AB  - Objective: The new sugarcane variety was bred, which had high-yield, high-sugar, lodging-resistant and suitable for mechanized production, in order to provide improved variety and technical support for sustainable development of Guangxi and even China cane sugar industry. Method: Using ROC22 as female parent and Guitang92-66 as male parent, the new variety Guitang04-1001 (also known as Guitang 42) was bred systematically through sexual hybridization and "Five-nursery System" breeding procedure. Then morphological characteristics and production characteristics were evaluated synthetically in the regional trial and production trial. Results: The results showed that Guitang 42 was characterized by high plant, medium-large stem, easy defoliation, high germination rate, moderate tillering ability, high stem forming rate, moderate resistance to smut, high resistance to mosaic and top rot, high drought resistance, and good ratooning ability. During "Five-nursery System" breeding procedure, the average yields of cane and sugar were 95.06-108.87 and 15.11-16.85 t/ha, increased by 11.3%-14.1% and 16.0%-18.9% compared with those of CK, respectively. In addition, in regional trials during 2011-2012, the average yields of cane and sugar were 101.70 and 15.03 t/ha, which were increased by 9.26% and 14.45% compared with CK, respectively, and the sucrose content was 14.77%, which was higher 0.66% (absolute value) than that of CK. In production trial in 2012, the average yield of cane was 88.62 t/ha, which were increased by 7.86% compared with that of CK. Furthermore, Guitang 42 was approved by Guangxi Crop Variety Approval Committee in 2013, and which was elected into catalogue of ten main sugarcane commercial varieties from Guangxi improved seed propagation system in 2014. Conclusion: Guitang 42 is characterized by early maturity, high yield, high sugar content, good lodging-resistant and ratooning abilities. Therefore, which is new variety with excellent comprehensive performance, and suited to be extended and planted in sugarcane area of south China.
